@58000 = ~My <PRO_LADYLORD>, I see you are travelling alone. Is there a specific reason for it?~
@58001 = ~It just so happened. That doesn't mean I will always be on my own.~
@58002 = ~Well, I don't like to depend on others.~
@58003 = ~I'm in pursuit of a very powerful wizard who has taken something vital from me. I don't want to endanger anyone else, if possible.~
@58004 = ~I'm following a dangerous person who took something vital from me. I'll make progress much quicker if I travel alone.~
@58005 = ~I'm chasing a man who dared to harm me. I'll let nobody get in my way.~
@58006 = ~I'm fighting against powerful Bhaalspawns and I don't want to endanger anyone else, if possible.~
@58007 = ~I'm fighting to become the next god of murder and I'll let nobody get in my way.~
@58008 = ~This is something I haven't really thought about.~
@58009 = ~I don't really want talk about it.~
@58010 = ~I can sense your power, my <PRO_LADYLORD>. But having companions on your side may provide more than mere strength in your journey.~
@58011 = ~So you want to rely on your own skills? You have made a brave decision, but you appear strong enough to me.~
@58012 = ~I share your sentiment. I was travelling alone for the very same reason across the plains of Faerûn.~
@58013 = ~But even so, you should not underestimate the strength and toughness of your fellow adventurers. They have a will of their own and may be willing to risk their lives for your cause.~
@58014 = ~You may, indeed. But there are times when you have to face overwhelming obstacles which exceed even your own strength.~
@58015 = ~You should not underestimate the strength and toughness of your fellow adventurers. They have a will of their own and may help you to overcome your own troubles.~
@58016 = ~Yes, I can see that. You are strong and confident, handling all kinds of obstacles which are thrown in your way.~
@58017 = ~Very well. I don't want to press you for an answer, my <PRO_LADYLORD>.~
@58018 = ~You are a thoughtful person, my <PRO_LADYLORD>.~
@58019 = ~Whatever choice you will make, I am sure you will succeed in your quest, however difficult it may become.~
@58020 = ~My <PRO_LADYLORD>, I see you are not travelling alone.~
@58021 = ~Would you care to introduce your companions to me?~
@58022 = ~Sure, why not?~
@58023 = ~Why should I? You can do it yourself.~
