// Afaaq's Epilogues
@64090 = ~Afaaq continued his journey with <CHARNAME> which took them halfway across Faerûn and back. They defeated raiding parties of sahuagin on the western borders of Tethyr and pushed back an invasion of frost giants threatening Luskan and the surrounding settlements.

Eventually Afaaq parted with <CHARNAME> and returned to his home on the Elemental Plane of Air at long last where he hoped to live a quiet life. But news of his deeds had even reached the ears of the Grand Caliph who offered him a position as advisor in mortal affairs at the Court of Ice and Steel.

However, as much as his time allows it, he takes the chance and travels across Faerûn in search of his kinsmen still waiting to be released from their imprisonments.~
@64091 = ~Afaaq left <CHARNAME> immediately after this event, returning to the Elemental Plane of Air at long last where he hoped to live a quiet life. But news of his deeds had even reached the ears of the Grand Caliph who offered him a position as advisor in mortal affairs at the Court of Ice and Steel.

